data.description: **Prime Location Alert! Your Dream Home Awaits in Grosse Pointe Farms.** Nestled in the heart of Grosse Pointe Farms, this property presents a unique opportunity to own a home strategically situated within walking distance of The Hills. Located right on the corner of this street, The Hills offers a vibrant array of shopping, dining, and entertainment options, adding to the allure of this exceptional neighborhood.  Featuring a well-thought-out floor plan, this home encompasses a first-floor bedroom, an inviting eat-in kitchen, a separate dining room, a spacious second floor, and the convenience of a 3-car garage. With such a versatile layout, the possibilities for transforming this space into your dream home are endless.  While this property already boasts an array of desirable features, it eagerly awaits your personal touch. This is your chance to infuse updates and unleash your creativity, turning this house into a home that perfectly reflects your style and preferences. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this prime location in Grosse Pointe Farms the backdrop for your next chapter.
